moji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n以下為植入式廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五毛電視 - 抵制tvb廣告商<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqBUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=a54e1731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a>"},{"pid":"553de3ec7c19c57b29106e07ff74dfb68f10e4e9","tid":1739246,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:13:33.000Z","msg":"我唔信"},{"pid":"fb304b6fee587dfba102fcbb483af6adf7728a58","tid":1739246,"uid":321374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"因為有回血劍<br />\n大把地可以強拆收回再賣<br />\n而且可以隨時㩒有錢係銀行既人轉錢入自己度<br />\n仲有大陸犯乜鳩法都係罰充公財產<br />\n<br />\n老共有一種搶人錢又唔會犯法既玩法<br />\n就係放縱一D厄錢，搶錢，偷錢既人<br />\n等佢偷到咁上下就一網打盡<br />\n罰既當然就係充公所得財產啦<br />\n<br />\n大陸其實只有9千萬人ja<br />\n其他果13億只係韭菜"}]}